data.description: Calling all Cash Buyers! This 3-bed, 2.5-bath gem features a family room with a cozy gas fireplace opening to the kitchen, creating the perfect gathering space. Upstairs, find the convenience of a utility room, 2 full baths, and a 1/2 bath on the main floor. With an attached 2-car garage a prime location close to shopping and Rt 23, this property offers both comfort and accessibility. Minor updates are all that's needed to make it your own. Don't let this opportunity slip away!
